item.description: Come join us for our third Wolfram|Alpha meetup! You will have the opportunity to discuss Wolfram|Alpha and its future with some of the Wolfram|Alpha developers. Come share your ideas and suggestions for future versions of Wolfram|Alpha and hear about new developments. We would also like to continue conversation about the use of Wolfram|Alpha as an educational tool. Of course, food and beverages will be provided!
item.name: Wolfram|Alpha Meetup
